Class QueryVCFDumper

java.lang.Object

      com.github.seqware.queryengine.system.exporters.QueryVCFDumper

public class QueryVCFDumper
extends Importer

Exporter using a new interface to the parameters in order to support queries triggerable from the command-line. Note that this will need to be run using the "hadoop jar" command instead of "java -classpath" when running in the large assembled jar file in the distribution folder
